title.rendered: BUSHWAKKA THE EXTREME DARKNESS AWNING – RHS (DRIVERS SIDE)

content.rendered:
Introducing the Bushwakka Extreme Darkness 270+

Talk about upgrades and Changing the Game…

The Extreme Darkness 270+ carries a well-developed ENDO FRAME, this gives our awnings the required strength to truly be freestanding.

Features & Inclusions:

Featuring all new built in LED lights with both White & Amber switches

900D Rip stop Polyester Canvas, water resistant and UV 50+

Aluminium Square Tube Framing

Black ENDO frame, backing plate and arms

1 x Built in leg – moveable to other arms

2 x Rope Ratchet

2 x Standard L Brackets – Will require rust treatment if located close to the coastline.

304 Stainless Steel bolts – Will require rust treatment if located close to the coastline.

Please note due to the size of this item it is pick up only from our store in Coffs Harbour. 

To see the full range of Bushwakka adventure gear available at Automax 4X4 click here.

Be sure to follow us on Facebook and Instagram to get your 4WD fix.
